{"tid":900463,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人仲記得【三人會議】","createTime":"2018-11-13T09:07:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-13T12:56:44.000Z","uid":20896,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0111cfb268e02d937b2a6485fa50a08e1e0d2f93","tid":900463,"uid":20896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T09:07:26.000Z","msg":"想當年，無咁先進<br />\n同班朋友打機，玩石器，玩童話，初初玩信長<br />\n<br />\n通常5-6個 有時玩信長更加有10個<br />\n<br />\n喂，你有無三人，駁比啊邊個啦<br />\n屌我無啊，你打完比佢，再打比我，再駁比C君<br />\n咁咪得囉撚樣<br />\n駁下駁下，駁到好多人<br />\n真正既會議<br />\n<br />\n跟住一傾就6-7個鐘，<br />\n屋企人同其他人永遠都打唔到返黎<br />\n有時吸埋左個電話，都唔識斷線<br />\n老母想打電話個陣，一拎起身聽<br />\n就聽到班朋友係到講粗口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n懷念以前既日子<br />\n大家開開心心打下機<br />\n無憂無慮"},{"pid":"618820821bf4263d7dcf8c3183adbbed598edb35","tid":900463,"uid":39072,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T09:08:51.000Z","msg":"就係因為三人會議打咗我千幾蚊電話費<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56639177aac905d0e475bd841a668e453aa0b56d","tid":900463,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T09:08:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7003adf10b548d5e621247880e865fda78ada3cf","tid":900463,"uid":92640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T09:10:21.000Z","msg":"以前打CS都係咁同FD打機<br />\n開擴音打機<br />\n<br />\n張仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf8b66665d5b8fc7744ad0a85d8feca00f891f6e","tid":900463,"uid":20896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"618820821bf4263d7dcf8c3183adbbed598edb35","tid":900463,"uid":39072,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T09:08:51.000Z","msg":"就係因為三人會議打咗我千幾蚊電話費<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"